members.member:

Is this IP Address less than or equal to the specified object IP Address?



true, when thisIPAddress 'less than equal to' objectIPAddress
/// thrown if the two IP Addresses are different lengths

member.example:
This should be instantiated within a using block so it is automatically disposed e.g.
using (new WaitCursor())
{
  // busy code goes here
}

example.code:
[BaseTypeRequired(typeof(IComponent)] // Specify requirement
public class ComponentAttribute : Attribute 
{}

[Component] // ComponentAttribute requires implementing IComponent interface
public class MyComponent : IComponent
{}
